# Notes based on AI Engineering book

Language Models
-Masked Language Model (predict missing tokens anywhere in a sequence, using the context from both before and after the missing tokens. Context -> surrounding tokens.)
-Autoregressive Language Model (predict the next token in a sequence using only the preceding tokens)

